                          "name": "intro_oe_routines_1",
                          "value": "Routines are intended to be 2 to 10 minute activities. However, they can be grouped to create open-ended explorations and good discussions of various topics. For example, a progression of Dot Cards can be used to emphasize a particular topic about quantities, subitizing, and unitizing.\n\nGo to the Routines section to find routines on any topic.",
